1
00:01:29,530 --> 00:01:33,180
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,670 --> 00:01:36,259
[Episode 23]

3
00:01:46,500 --> 00:01:47,180
Everyone.

4
00:01:47,470 --> 00:01:48,110
Tonight

5
00:01:48,140 --> 00:01:50,860
is the annual
Lantern Festival death match.

6
00:01:50,979 --> 00:01:54,140
It is also my wedding
as the Master of Lingya Tower.

7
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:56,200
And I hope

8
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:59,039
this thrilling hunt of life and death

9
00:01:59,220 --> 00:02:01,620
will help celebrate such a grand occasion.

10
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:04,220
Celebrate with all under heaven!

11
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:06,380
Eternal Prosperity of Lingya Tower!

12
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,920
Celebrate with all under heaven!

13
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:09,600
Eternal Prosperity of Lingya Tower!

14
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:10,840
Celebrate with all under heaven!

15
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,280
Eternal Prosperity of Lingya Tower!

16
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,650
Celebrate with all under heaven!

17
00:02:13,650 --> 00:02:15,030
Eternal Prosperity of Lingya Tower!

18
00:02:15,030 --> 00:02:17,800
This round of the death match
is called the Hunting Grounds.

19
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,730
The female prisoners are the prey.

20
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:22,600
One point for a hit with bow or crossbow.

21
00:02:22,640 --> 00:02:25,880
Two points for close-range injuries.

22
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:29,200
Five points for taking a head.

23
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:32,760
Whoever scores the highest by the end
will be crowned champion.

24
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:35,520
And rest assured, everyone.

25
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:39,000
All the prey have already
taken a muscle-weakening drug.

26
00:02:39,079 --> 00:02:41,010
They are completely defenseless.

27
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:43,360
So enjoy the hunt to your heart's content!

28
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:44,920
Where're my friends?

29
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:47,020
They're already here.

30
00:02:50,550 --> 00:02:51,350
Ah!

31
00:02:52,060 --> 00:02:53,500
Dao. Tuya.

32
00:02:53,530 --> 00:02:54,530
Nan Yanzhi.

33
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,280
Master!

34
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,520
Yanzhi!

35
00:03:02,820 --> 00:03:04,420
Why are they down there?

36
00:03:07,380 --> 00:03:10,140
Yanzhi, I promised you

37
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:11,520
I would not harm them.

38
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:14,960
I said they would
appear alive at our wedding.

39
00:03:15,180 --> 00:03:18,500
But whether they survive
this round of the death match

40
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:21,500
depends on their fate.

41
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,640
You lied to me!

42
00:03:27,230 --> 00:03:30,000
From now on,
if our world holds only each other,

43
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,730
that wouldn't be so bad.

44
00:03:36,130 --> 00:03:37,570
Despicable!

45
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:44,480
Everyone, the grand annual
Lantern Festival death match,

46
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:45,680
the Hunting Grounds,

47
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:47,600
begins now!

48
00:04:00,170 --> 00:04:00,960
Master!

49
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,800
Please be careful!

50
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:26,120
What's going on?

51
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:29,260
Weren't they given
the muscle-weakening drug?

52
00:04:31,350 --> 00:04:35,220
[Elite Academy]

53
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:41,080
Officer Qin.

54
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,060
And all of you...

55
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,640
Bet you didn't expect this, Nan Yanzhi.

56
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:48,640
The two of us have been
helping you in secret all along.

57
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:52,720
On the night of the Lantern Festival,

58
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:56,080
most of the tower's guards
will be gathered at the Hunting Grounds.

59
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:59,440
That will be the perfect chance
to unlock the prison cells on every floor

60
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:01,680
and lead everyone out of Lingya Tower.

61
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:03,440
Every year, the muscle-weakening drug
given to the female prisoners

62
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,890
is prepared by me.

63
00:05:05,050 --> 00:05:06,160
And this year is no exception.

64
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:08,400
Once chaos erupts in the Hunting Grounds,

65
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,760
we'll coordinate with you.

66
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:10,800
We'll open the cells on every floor

67
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,890
and release all the female prisoners.

68
00:05:11,890 --> 00:05:14,400
By then, our people
will disguise themselves as nobles

69
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:15,560
and slip into the crowd.

70
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:17,210
With our forces working inside and out,

71
00:05:17,210 --> 00:05:18,990
we'll definitely succeed in one strike.

72
00:05:18,990 --> 00:05:19,710
Mm.

73
00:05:26,020 --> 00:05:26,820
Nan Yanzhi.

74
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,790
Nan Yanzhi.

75
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,490
You're still alive!

76
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,800
Keep your voice down.

77
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:36,840
This is my master.

78
00:05:40,700 --> 00:05:41,850
Master?

79
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,050
I owe you an apology.

80
00:05:43,100 --> 00:05:46,159
For the sake of the plan,
I had to hide my identity.

81
00:05:46,230 --> 00:05:47,230
So it was you.

82
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,200
Dao.

83
00:05:49,260 --> 00:05:50,050
Tuya.

84
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,320
Jiang Man?

85
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:54,980
What are you doing here?

86
00:05:54,980 --> 00:05:56,290
Earlier, when Man broke the bowl,

87
00:05:56,290 --> 00:05:58,000
I was the one who told her to do it.

88
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,650
Sorry for not telling you beforehand.

89
00:05:59,650 --> 00:06:00,980
You actually lied to us.

90
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:05,920
I knew it.

91
00:06:07,250 --> 00:06:08,800
There's no way you were smart enough

92
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,330
to betray us all of a sudden.

93
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:13,560
This time,

94
00:06:13,730 --> 00:06:15,080
we're not only here to save you.

95
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:16,500
We're here to save everyone.

96
00:06:16,500 --> 00:06:17,060
Mm.

97
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:18,680
Once the death match begins,

98
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:21,040
the three of you lead everyone out.

99
00:06:21,060 --> 00:06:22,120
What about you two?

100
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:24,660
I'm going to destroy Lingya Tower

101
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:27,060
and wipe out these monsters for good.

102
00:06:27,180 --> 00:06:28,140
Count me in.

103
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:29,360
But if you stay,

104
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:31,220
you'll be facing a perilous battle.

105
00:06:31,220 --> 00:06:32,580
The warriors of my tribe

106
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:34,040
do not retreat.

107
00:06:34,330 --> 00:06:36,110
And we would never abandon our comrades.

108
00:06:36,110 --> 00:06:37,440
I'm not leaving either.

109
00:06:37,620 --> 00:06:38,740
If I ran away now,

110
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:41,440
I probably wouldn't sleep peacefully
for the rest of my life.

111
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:43,740
Anyway, we either live together

112
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:44,960
or die together.

113
00:06:44,980 --> 00:06:45,780
Mm.

114
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:48,720
I'll fight alongside Yanzhi too.

115
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:51,440
In that case,

116
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:55,680
then we live and die together.

117
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,320
Fight through death to live.

118
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,160
Live and die together!

119
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,760
Fight through death to live!

120
00:07:07,290 --> 00:07:08,170
Everyone!

121
00:07:08,980 --> 00:07:11,120
The time for revenge has come!

122
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:16,910
Kill!

123
00:07:20,020 --> 00:07:20,990
Archers, fire!

124
00:08:30,570 --> 00:08:31,380
Go, now!

125
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:38,640
Hurry!

126
00:08:39,530 --> 00:08:40,169
This way!

127
00:09:10,490 --> 00:09:14,680
Kill!

128
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:18,210
Prime Minister!

129
00:09:18,560 --> 00:09:19,490
Prime Minister!

130
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:20,740
Prime Minister!

131
00:09:20,740 --> 00:09:23,470
The female prisoners
in the tower have revolted!

132
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:26,000
Quick! Notify the nearby
prefectures at once!

133
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,920
Tell them to send
reinforcements immediately!

134
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:28,600
Yes, Sir!

135
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,040
Master, over here!

136
00:09:53,250 --> 00:09:54,580
Kill!

137
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,650
Go after Prime Minister Lin.

138
00:10:11,650 --> 00:10:12,640
Leave him to me.

139
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,120
Nan Yanzhi,

140
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:27,940
why are you still so stubborn?

141
00:10:28,640 --> 00:10:30,300
I'll give you one last chance.

142
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:32,400
Come back to my side right now.

143
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:34,640
You're just as rotten as Lingya Tower now.

144
00:10:34,640 --> 00:10:35,980
Even if I die,

145
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:38,320
I will never be with you.

146
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,800
Nan Yanzhi!

147
00:11:21,290 --> 00:11:25,730
Kill!

148
00:11:29,170 --> 00:11:32,410
Kill!

149
00:11:51,860 --> 00:11:52,890
Zhuang Wujiu.

150
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:55,300
Spare my life,

151
00:11:56,450 --> 00:11:58,600
and I can erase your criminal status.

152
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:02,140
I can even grant you
a position of honor and prestige.

153
00:12:02,530 --> 00:12:05,520
Then you'll be admired
by all under heaven.

154
00:12:05,540 --> 00:12:06,620
Ha!

155
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:09,040
What good is fine silk and glory?

156
00:12:09,230 --> 00:12:10,830
What good is endless wealth?

157
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:13,390
None of it can erase
the pain I've endured all my life.

158
00:12:13,390 --> 00:12:15,920
None of it can cover up
the filth of this world.

159
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:19,200
Then what is it you want?

160
00:12:20,350 --> 00:12:22,080
As long as it's within my power,

161
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,740
I'll give it to you.

162
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:27,620
For all the suffering
and injustice we endured,

163
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:30,120
even if I'm torn to pieces...

164
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:38,600
I'll make you pay in blood!

165
00:13:03,770 --> 00:13:04,650
Hyah!

166
00:13:06,410 --> 00:13:07,410
Hyah!

167
00:13:34,040 --> 00:13:38,810
♪ Frost still lights the old road,
while hatred traps my disciple ♪

168
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:45,870
♪ Back then, you reached for me
with tears in your eyes ♪

169
00:13:47,570 --> 00:13:53,560
♪ I wiped your tears away
and carried your future on my shoulders ♪

170
00:13:54,870 --> 00:14:01,190
♪ I'd trade half my life
just to see you safe ♪

171
00:14:02,380 --> 00:14:05,050
♪ Your kindness is carved into my heart,
so I dared to challenge fate ♪

172
00:14:06,140 --> 00:14:08,680
♪ In this cruel world,
you were my only warmth ♪

173
00:14:09,700 --> 00:14:11,880
♪ You taught me to wield my sword through
the fog and led me out of darkness ♪

174
00:14:12,680 --> 00:14:15,730
♪ You showed me
that loyalty outweighs life itself ♪

175
00:14:19,540 --> 00:14:22,840
♪ Ours is a bond of souls,
and the greatest gift of all ♪

176
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,120
Master,

177
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:24,260
when will you start teaching me?

178
00:14:23,900 --> 00:14:26,390
♪ I once swore to protect you
until you found freedom ♪

179
00:14:24,520 --> 00:14:26,740
When did I ever agree
to take you as my disciple?

180
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:29,440
Master, please teach me
the strongest martial arts!

181
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:30,050
♪ Though my sins can never be repaid,
I still tend your wounds ♪

182
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:31,780
I want to avenge my parents!

183
00:14:30,970 --> 00:14:33,770
♪ I only pray Heaven
never leaves you alone again ♪

184
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:33,330
I made this for you, Master.

185
00:14:33,350 --> 00:14:36,430
I named it the filigree bangle.

186
00:14:34,610 --> 00:14:37,290
♪ Now that revenge is won,
my heart feels emptier than ever ♪

187
00:14:36,760 --> 00:14:38,920
One day, when you wear it,

188
00:14:38,220 --> 00:14:40,770
♪ What I fear most is you
sacrificing yourself for me in the end ♪

189
00:14:38,950 --> 00:14:40,920
if we charge into Lingya Tower together,

190
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:42,000
nothing will stand in our way.

191
00:14:41,610 --> 00:14:44,370
♪ Even if fate leaves us no road ahead ♪

192
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,260
We'll be unstoppable.

193
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:49,710
♪ I still wish to face
this doomed path by your side ♪

194
00:15:05,530 --> 00:15:08,550
♪ The wind cuts like blades,
the night feels like a grave ♪

195
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:09,210
Why didn't you kill me back then?

196
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,600
Why?

197
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:12,350
♪ Together we walked
through blood and chaos ♪

198
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:15,580
♪ Our hearts bound as one,
our fates intertwined ♪

199
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:20,260
♪ Our vow was carved deep into our palms ♪

200
00:15:21,690 --> 00:15:24,730
♪ If not for you, how could I
stand tall within the flames? ♪

201
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:25,950
Other than you,

202
00:15:25,590 --> 00:15:28,360
♪ Without your protection,
I'd never have made it this far ♪

203
00:15:27,310 --> 00:15:29,060
I have nothing left to hold onto.

204
00:15:29,060 --> 00:15:31,720
[Virtue and Merit in Equal Splendor]

205
00:15:29,180 --> 00:15:32,070
♪ The one who escaped the prison,
the one who forged the sword ♪

206
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:35,440
♪ Together we walked
through blades and fire as one ♪

207
00:15:35,940 --> 00:15:37,690
You don't have to hesitate
because of me anymore.

208
00:15:37,690 --> 00:15:40,430
♪ Falling into the snow ♪

209
00:15:37,900 --> 00:15:39,560
Stop carrying everything alone.

210
00:15:39,560 --> 00:15:41,660
I want to fight by your side.

211
00:15:42,060 --> 00:15:45,860
♪ Your eyes reflect our final farewell ♪

212
00:15:42,430 --> 00:15:43,250
For my parents,

213
00:15:43,250 --> 00:15:44,090
and for you,

214
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:47,000
let's make them repay every debt they owe.

215
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:48,700
If Lingya Tower didn't
exist in this world,

216
00:15:48,700 --> 00:15:53,330
♪ Master, stay awake.
I still want to hear my name from you ♪

217
00:15:48,830 --> 00:15:51,990
I really would like
to stay here with you forever.

218
00:15:52,400 --> 00:15:53,400
Then tonight,

219
00:15:53,420 --> 00:15:54,640
let's pretend

220
00:15:55,070 --> 00:15:56,760
that none of this exists.

221
00:15:55,620 --> 00:16:00,880
♪ Don’t cry, disciple.
I'd protect you through every lifetime ♪

222
00:15:57,130 --> 00:15:58,210
No tower.

223
00:15:58,320 --> 00:15:59,720
No cages.

224
00:16:00,160 --> 00:16:01,590
Only wine.

225
00:16:01,660 --> 00:16:04,700
♪ Only now do I understand ♪

226
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:06,600
Only you and me.

227
00:16:05,660 --> 00:16:08,500
♪ The hottest, deepest, fiercest feeling ♪

228
00:16:09,420 --> 00:16:12,900
♪ Is this very moment ♪

229
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:20,240
♪ This life is enough.
This life is enough ♪

230
00:16:21,090 --> 00:16:23,360
♪ It began with passion and ended in joy ♪

231
00:16:24,340 --> 00:16:27,110
♪ May we still protect each other
as master and disciple in the next life ♪

232
00:16:28,300 --> 00:16:31,110
♪ And walk together to the end
of the road we never finished ♪

233
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:31,920
Master...

234
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:37,770
♪ Snow buries our names ♪

235
00:16:33,230 --> 00:16:34,450
They

236
00:16:35,350 --> 00:16:36,950
came to save us.

237
00:16:39,710 --> 00:16:43,630
♪ May the wind remember their brave ♪

238
00:16:43,700 --> 00:16:44,800
Nan Yanzhi!

239
00:16:44,880 --> 00:16:45,420
Yanzhi!

240
00:16:45,190 --> 00:16:49,890
♪ Silhouettes ♪

241
00:16:45,450 --> 00:16:46,180
Miss Zhuang!

242
00:16:46,900 --> 00:16:47,370
Yanzhi!

243
00:16:47,380 --> 00:16:48,110
Miss Zhuang!

244
00:16:48,130 --> 00:16:48,770
Miss Zhuang!

245
00:16:48,770 --> 00:16:49,500
Nan Yanzhi!

246
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:50,970
-Nan Yanzhi!
-Zhuang Wujiu!

247
00:16:50,970 --> 00:16:51,770
Zhuang Wujiu!

248
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:55,980
You fulfilled the promise
you made to everyone.

249
00:16:55,980 --> 00:16:57,950
I won't let anything happen to you.

250
00:16:58,660 --> 00:16:59,850
We succeeded.

251
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:01,720
Yes, Yanzhi.

252
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:02,960
Look!

253
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:04,849
Everyone escaped from Lingya Tower!

